	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habeo magnam gratiam pro rebus novis, quas ex amicorum literis mihi significasti, idque ut saepe, ac quotiescunque graviores occupationes te non ret(inent), modo aliquid habeas, facias rogo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ante literas quoque eas acceperam, quibus de vestri magistratus circa indicenda vel non indicenda potius comitia deliberation(...) me certiorem faciebas.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ac scito tamen a [me] tum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l300" cert="high">Lucernenses</placeName> tum alios quoque ex Confoe(deratis) petivisse, ut ea, si possem, per <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinos</placeName> cura(rem) indicenda.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si nolint, ego spero per alios me ef(fecturum); sed propter aliquas causas rem non putavi nimis accelerandam.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> habe(mus) <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7255">ducem Ferrariensem</persName> maxima damna <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1122">Parmens(i)</placeName> intulisse multaque castella in eius ditione partim vi partim deditione cepisse et inter ea unum tum maximi momenti tum egregie munitum, (quo) occupato totus ager <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1122">Parmensis</placeName> mirum in modum infestatur.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Id ipse <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7255">dux Ferrariensis</persName> mihi scrip(sit).</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero me habiturum successorem ita utrique nostrum amicum, ut alia ratio, qua saepius per literas invisere nos possimus, ineunda non sit, quam ut ad illum semper literae dirigantur.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quia tamen nondum certus sum, nomen eius non scribo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Cupio d. consulem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1419">Habium</persName> meo nomine salutari.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l760" cert="high">Solodori</placeName> calendas martii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8183" cert="high">Sanlaurent[ianus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[vor 389:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo the(o)logo et amicissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[von anderer Hand:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An herren <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrich Bullinger</persName> <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
